      "content": "That's a great start, it really captures the tone. Can you expand on it? Maybe have him describe the people they've encountered more specifically. He's been observing them from a distance, and he's making some observations about their customs, their appearance, and why he thinks they're fundamentally unable to govern themselves without European guidance.",
